headline: Exploring Analyst Estimates for Cencora (COR) Q1 Earnings, Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Cencora (COR), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended December 2025.
